ActFederal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
SubjectAgreements amending the TAX COLLECTION AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the Province of each Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Manitoba, British Columbia, Prince Edward Island, Saskatchewan, Alberta, Newfoundland and Labrador, Yukon and Nunavut,
PrecisApproval of an Order authorizing the Minister of Finance, on behalf of the Government of Canada, to enter into agreements to amend the TAX COLLECTION AGREEMENTS with the government of each of Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Manitoba, British Columbia, Prince Edward Island, Saskatchewan, Alberta, Newfoundland and Labrador, Yukon and Nunavut.
